assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a5260cf4007e07494966cd1d98a728c4ea9b080","tid":51131,"uid":6455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T05:16:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">加油， 腹膜炎大左會冇事， 我朋友隻貓撐到3歲幾後來好得返。</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n希望會有奇蹟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我同上天講 我短命啲都想佢好番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n樓上個朋友應該係乾性腹膜炎<br />\n樓主係濕性冇得搞"},{"pid":"9626ac24ba42cffcd8b48f4243fb67e7dca164e6","tid":51131,"uid":44655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T16:37:10.000Z","msg":"想問下樓主貓貓最後咩情況？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}